   <text>
      <body>
         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">[Melbourne] ¶  7 August 1860 ¶ 3986 ¶ Sir, ¶  ¶ Yr ¶  letter of the 17th Ulto ¶  requesting that when the present lease of the toll on the St Kilda road expires permission may be granted for the passa...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="Progress%20note"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; color: #0000ff; "
               xml:lang="en">Delete [Melbourne]?</p>
            <p rend="Progress%20note"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; color: #0000ff; "
               xml:lang="en">Fn 7: information would be useful, but not necessary to understand the letter.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">60.08.07</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">From Thomas Balmain</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">No. 60/2557, unit 6, p. 38, VPRS 975/P1 outward registered correspondence, <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>VA 669 Department of Public Works, Public Record Office, Victoria.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="font-weight: bold; ">To proof.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>[Melbourne]<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="font-style: italic; ">editorial addition</seg>
                  </p>
               </note> 7 August 1860</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">3986</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Yr<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">Your.</p>
               </note> letter of the 17th Ulto<note xml:id="ftn4" type="footnote" n="4">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">M to J. Francis, 17 July 1860.</p>
               </note> requesting that when the present lease of the toll on the St Kilda road expires permission may be granted for the passage of the vehicles of Visitors to the Botanic Gardens through the Govt reserve near Princes Bridge, having been submitted for the consideration of the Bd of L &amp; Works,<note xml:id="ftn5" type="footnote" n="5">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">Board of Land and Works.</p>
               </note> I am desired to inform you that the Bd<note xml:id="ftn6" type="footnote" n="6">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="font-weight: bold; ">check minutes of Bd at PRO and cite them.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note> cannot provide funds or in any way encourage the idea of forming a road through the reserve in question.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">Sd TC Balmain [secy]</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">The Director of the Botanic Gardens</p>
         </div>
